{
  "stem": "3631.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there we saw, while we were waiting-- they kept us there until the whole thing was over, and then we could go back to our homes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "While we were waiting, there was a, a children's home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We saw how a truck pulled up, and the Germans went up into this children's home and, and threw the children down on the truck.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was a-- the other angle of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then you kept on living for the next thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, I've seen shootings and beatings, plenty beatings.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've seen when we first-- no, that was in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was plenty beating and plenty shooting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were big Aktion-- whenever there were these Aktions, there was always-- people were shot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think that, in the ghetto in Cracow-- if I may talk about Schindler for a moment-- he already employed people in his satellite camp in, in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he was friends with [NON-ENGLISH], and he, he would go on horseback one side of the ghetto where, where, where there was a hill, and he would stand on top of the hill.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think they showed this in the movie, where he looked down and saw what was going on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think it was that point that Hitler began to see that it was-- that the Jews were not only a money-making proposition, but that he had to-- he would try to save them.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I knew some.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See in the first, they all lived in the ghetto, and they moved.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came out in the morning and came back at night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Only later on, he established his own little camp where he kept them overnight.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
